 2024-12392024-11-22AAFC
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Provision of Non-Repayable Contributions to Dairy Processors
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide NON-REPAYABLE CONTRIBUTIONS of up to $14.95 million to DAIRY PROCESORS to assist in managing a growing surplus of non-fat milk solids and compensate for market losses as a result of the Canada-United States-Mexico Agreement.
